{"tid":1542332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[831恐襲] 有好幾條問題想消防解釋，破案關鍵","createTime":"2019-09-04T22:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:49:34.000Z","uid":20414,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e19e7c90755d44920f37c188cf49fab329eae95","tid":1542332,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:31:54.000Z","msg":"事緣尋日明報有一篇報導<br />\n<br />\n//網上流傳8月31日衝突中，港鐵太子站共有10名傷者，而消防處當晚僅運送7名傷者至兩間醫院，3名重傷者不知所蹤，流傳有死者被送往廣華醫院殮房，又稱有屍體被抛出公海等。消防處今日（4日）回覆《明報》查詢時表示，當晚初步點算有10名傷者，其後再次點算確認7人需送院，或因傷者曾換位而重複計算，或指揮官再次確認人數時有傷者表示不需救護服務，導致兩次點算結果不同。//"},{"pid":"62bddc9e73fa5a5fb297a1301b8929fa5c6275f4","tid":1542332,"uid":20414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:32:56.000Z","msg":"1）消防一定有紀錄，出左幾多部車，去過邊度同車上人員既走動<br />\n2）如是者，點解會叫大型醫療車，咩根據？七個傷者出大車做分流？<br />\n3）好啦，太子封站，冇人上黎，咁我想問，落左去既救護員，究竟跟車去左荔枝角定邊度？<br />\n4）如果跟左架地鐵走，即係佢棄左架車係太子。如果冇跟走，咁中間個真空期車箱係唔係冇救護員？<br />\n5）架車去左邊間醫院，唔係同我講唔知呀嗎<br />\n6）最重要係，人證講既消防員係邊度出黎？<br />\n<br />\n所以追住消防咬一定有料到<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗，有料我會 fwd 俾記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aab6985c6993950e25aa3096aee23b462ccf53","tid":1542332,"uid":4213,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:53:39.000Z","msg":"提各位智力較低嘅港豬<br />\n知道你地好嬲<br />\n應該有人直頭想用血來報復<br />\n<br />\n但記住<br />\n就算真相係點都好<br />\n而家都係「推測」有示威者比人打死左<br />\n如果係呢個時期有狗仔真係死左<br />\n成件事會唔同晒<br />\n<br />\n因為如果新聞講「狗隻死亡」先過「示威者死亡」<br />\n成個感情道德上 狗隻會拎返唔少分"},{"pid":"423421ac694b0b972f65d7feff8f40964700c1b0","tid":1542332,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"221f7a56db5b5a91b7789728e3d71124669c561d","tid":1542332,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:04:27.000Z","msg":"真心要解答下<br />\n同埋搵番個晚係太子既人"},{"pid":"dbe78243c32b41bf583d497a1d1bce4c79afe623","tid":1542332,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:06:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"eba5afa7544f971697f0968c6012cacae02e9e29","tid":1542332,"uid":133606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:11:27.000Z","msg":"救護好似係 under 消防署"},{"pid":"94d3503f751f795aa2ff23e625d8710dfbf2ff9f","tid":1542332,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:20:43.000Z","msg":"塔利班記招答咗你大部分問題, 建議睇完先再問"},{"pid":"40db0f8b2d53415004973fa9bcc345b9c6204aa6","tid":1542332,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"如果冇當日既消防出黎講真聲，我宣傳消防同狗冇分別"},{"pid":"47e3786f0d375188aab76acb75971f19fc1e3488","tid":1542332,"uid